==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ingenuously
<hw>In*gen"u*ous*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In an ingenuous manner;
openly; fairly; candidly; artlessly.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Being required to explain himself, he <qex>ingenuously</qex>
confessed.</q> <rj><qau>Ludlow.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ingenuousness</ent>⟦br⟧
